              <title>Moodle launches its first official MOOC with teachers in mind</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8518</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/8518</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>When I heard this news, I'm so exerciting.</p>]]></description>
