<p><strong>Context: </strong>Ski patrol Pre Hospital Emergency care course.</p>
<p><strong>Tools:</strong> I have access to Moodle with a few question addons (the drag and drop types from the OU: https://moodle.org/plugins/browse.php?list=category&amp;id=29<br />Trying to avoid complext tools so tutors can actually tweak questions/add/reuse questions etc.</p>
