              <title>Moodle and Cloudworks</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2574</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/2574</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[<p>Sorry if you came here thinking it was an answer.&nbsp; It isn't yet!</p>
<p>I started this cloud to discuss what an integration should look like and how Moodle can help to work on it.</p>
<p>I guess the simplest integration would be to treat this site as a big repository of clouds/cloudscapes/tags/people, and create a Moodle repository plugin that basically does what the search box here does, until you get to a page you want, and then that URL is passed back to the 'url' activity in Moodle, so that cloudworks pages can be easily added into Moodle courses.</p>
<p>That's probably not enough, I'm guessing.&nbsp; What else can we do?&nbsp; What else would people want?</p><p>Contact details: here</p>]]></description>
